        <div class="intro__description">
          <h1 class="float"><b>Hi there,</b></h1>
          <h3>My name's Joseph.</h3>
          <h5><i>I like to code, play chess, and laugh.</i></h5>
          <p>Problems have all sorts of solutions. Like in art, how solutions are expressed depends on the user behind the code.
            While programming will always has myraid of questions to be discovered, the best questions sit brewing in the back of my head.
            After all, only good questions can bear fruit to good answers.</p>
          <p>For me there's nothing quite like finding a simple solution to a complex problem.
            Sometimes I love the feeling when thought immerses me completely. As a child I'd could sit down for hours with a new book.
            There was something about the creak of the pages, the texture of pressed sheets, and the scent of freshly printed paper that kept me hooked to my imagination.</p>
        </div>
